query: INSERT INTO product_categories (productId, categoryId) SELECT DISTINCT p.id, 60003 FROM products p WHERE p.brand IN ('Waters', 'Phenomenex') AND (LOWER(p.name) LIKE '%screw cap%' OR LOWER(p.name) LIKE '%septa%') AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM product_categories pc WHERE pc.productId = p.id AND pc.categoryId = 60003);
